0-02-05T04:23:56.000Z","msg":"2019 Novel Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) <br />\nHospital Preparedness Checklist pdf icon<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/hcp/hcp-hospital-checklist.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fcoronavirus%2F2019-ncov%2Fhcp%2Fhcp-hospital-checklist.html&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3c2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=c920943d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/hcp/hcp-hospital-checklist.html</a>"},{"pid":"89ef9e3d33e3e87032cf59bcf8746b82d9488c76","tid":1862570,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76c27222db402f393e5bc3eb657823f47ccb139","tid":1862570,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ec614a1a9724f3308107ddd98d4878affd8db24","tid":1862570,"uid":119875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:35:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你們知不知道一旦爆發，你們復工等於害己又害人。</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"係隔離營當值既姑娘有野想同大家講<br />\n<br />\n姑娘入營係要一齊入去住<br />\n間房就係懷疑染病、被隔離既病人附近<br />\n做野已經驚中招<br />\n休息訓覺都感受到個種壓迫感<br />\n<br />\n而且營入面既衞生又唔好<br />\n床單又有漬 又唔知有無消毒<br />\n完全得唔到充分休息<br />\n<br />\n我地原本係衛生署姑娘<br />\n入營第一日返9am-5pm<br />\n第二日就由2pm去到第三日既11am <br />\n足足係21個小時困係入面!!!! <br />\n<br />\n之後果日就要返clinic接觸公眾<br />\n係！你無聽錯<br />\n我地係直出番社區clinic<br />\n衞生署clinic包咩？<br />\n就係咩都有！普通市民又有<br />\n公務員診所又有<br />\n母嬰健康院都係衛生署！<br />\n好擔心自己做左超級病毒傳播員😭<br />\n<br />\n我幾辛苦都好 都一定會同大家打贏場瘟疫<br />\n林鄭呢條仆街真係想香港人攬炒<br />\n係手足既！同我share呢個消息出去！<br />\n大家出少d街 照顧好自己就幫到我地<br />\n<br />\n立即封關 罷工救港<br />\n康復香港 時代抗疫<br />\n<br />\n#手足投稿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/c/1307213416/13596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1307213416%2F13596&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3c2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=19756c72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1307213416/13596</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqaB3Ge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqaB3Ge.jpg&h=bfe106e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GKV6GsV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGKV6GsV.jpg&h=1e16a0da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d161b4487f2a489018729daf7628ab52516f711","tid":1862570,"uid":263197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ed558d99f9dd6cffc8b3804a14107458a7a261","tid":1862570,"uid":207614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:35:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98f8ee6e0037e8a8553707f09169f29b9075f34f","tid":1862570,"uid":119875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:24:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9db63bcbcbf5a907ad9da03cd9c7b75cc51d5df","tid":1862570,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86ed558d99f9dd6cffc8b3804a14107458a7a261","tid":1862570,"uid":207614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:35:35.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:25:34.000Z","msg":"多謝推"},{"pid":"c4c78c2f275c270c3782a7a386b23d573ee29668","tid":1862570,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:26:47.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好心軟呀，林奠而家就係睇死你地會返黎先放慢黎玩咋"},{"pid":"542bd8759bf6eb3dc75d75acf975a0a1da54ce02","tid":1862570,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f786190f2e85ab5555966a3dcc9f0f13bb29230e","tid":1862570,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aac02f854a16a6acb50616c7c675795b4463dbc6","tid":1862570,"uid":73143,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:47:15.000Z","msg":"[全民三罷] 醫護工會並不代表所有 醫護，以及 香港人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eQoLAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eQoLAS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>上醫醫國，中醫醫人，下醫醫病</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n鑑於太多吹風唔罷<br />\n我想講既係醫護罷工起左個頭後，好多工會都準備緊<br />\n香港人要做既係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全港大三罷</span></span></strong><br />\n直至政府做返本身佢應該要做既事，甚至係五大訴求<br />\n成個制度已經由內至外腐爛，一日唔改變都只會有同樣既事情發生<br />\n而唔係咩社區大爆發之後成班返去醫院醫病<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醫護工會並不代表所有醫護，以及 香港人<br />\n<br />\n妥協只會失敗</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzWp8d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzWp8d0.png&h=12ec3a53&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:48:30.000Z","msg":"MBBS cert<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:29:32.000Z","msg":"其實佢又冇話張cert係佢"},{"pid":"1f63e18846544a51962dfc0fa943904f26a99045","tid":1862570,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:40:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d1e8d3df4e9c701912f42d05d7362b9e6a0eab70","tid":1862570,"uid":119875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f47d1b25c8e1ad68d46e12479fa60de811cc0f","tid":1862570,"uid":246329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:07:58.000Z","msg":"高汁文 推"},{"pid":"8026b9daccd954abc75d49b46e3d3ecf2c2d0e06","tid":1862570,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:17:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95f85ad240d55c34a6c29616326d13cdf7ca055e","tid":1862570,"uid